  'Are low fat foods healthy?Not necessarily.It can be tempting when trying to lose weight to be lured in by the marketing strategies on the front of â€œlow fatâ€ foods however, these foods tend to be m',
  '<h2>Are low fat foods healthy?</h2><p><strong>Not necessarily.</strong></p><p>It can be tempting when trying to lose weight to be lured in by the marketing strategies on the front of â€œlow fatâ€ foods however, these foods tend to be much higher in sugar and salt to make them taste nicer.</p><p>Itâ€™s actually better to have the unaltered version without all the added sugar and salt but have a bit less of it!Â </p>',
  'Craig Blackman',
  'General',
  false,
  '2022-03-29 09:04:34'
